Title: Amuse-Bouche
Plot: Will Graham, now an official special investigator with the FBI, helps Jack Crawford and the BAU unit search for a murderer who buries his victims alive to use as fertilizer. Tabloid journalist, Freddie Lounds, sets her sights on Will.
GuestStars: Scott Thompson, Aaron Abrams, Kacey Rohl, Lara Jean Chorostecki, Aidan Devine
